\pc \bd 22\bd*

\s Ee Bwana, tunasifu Mapendo yako
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ee Bwana, tunasifu \bd*\bd Mapendo \bd*\bd yako sana Tunashangaa kweli, tunapokutazama\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Kwa sisi ulikuja kwa kutukufilia, Tupate usamehe, tufike kwako\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd .\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Taraja yetu iko kufika kwako, Bwana, Na kutazama uso waliouumiza\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Faraja ya mioyo na sifa ya midomo Katika majaribu, furaha na salama.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mwokozi wetu Yesu, pokea shukurani. Uliyevumilia makosa, haya vile\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na sasa unangoja kutufikisha kwako\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Unastahili kweli kupata utukufu.\bd*
